<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>{title} - 프로젝트 포트폴리오</title>
    <script
      src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/js/all.min.js"
    ></script>
    <style is:global>
      :root {
        --primary-color: #003f88;
        --secondary-color: #00296b;
        --accent-color: #fdc500;
        --light-color: #f8f9fa;
        --dark-color: #212529;
        --table-header-bg: #003f88;
        --table-row-even: #e9ecef;
        --table-row-odd: #ffffff;
        --table-row-hover: #cfe2ff;
        --table-border: #dee2e6;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--dark-color);
        background-color: var(--light-color);
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .container {
        width: 95%;
        max-width: 1400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      header {
        background-color: var(--primary-color);
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem 0;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }

      .project-info {
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .project-description {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .table-container {
        overflow-x: auto;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .project-table {
        width: 100%;
        min-width: 1200px; /* 테이블의 최소 너비 설정 */
        table-layout: fixed;
      }

      .project-table th,
      .project-table td {
        padding: 12px 15px;
        text-align: left;
        font-size: 16px;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--table-border);
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        white-space: nowrap;
        overflow: hidden;
        text-overflow: ellipsis;
      }

      .project-table th {
        background-color: var(--table-header-bg);
        color: white;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      .project-table th:nth-child(1),
      .project-table td:nth-child(1) {
        width: 40px;
      } /* 연번 */
      .project-table th:nth-child(2),
      .project-table td:nth-child(2) {
        width: 90px;
      } /* 1Depth */
      .project-table th:nth-child(3),
      .project-table td:nth-child(3) {
        width: 120px;
      } /* 2Depth */
      .project-table th:nth-child(4),
      .project-table td:nth-child(4) {
        width: 120px;
      } /* Tab-Depth */
      .project-table th:nth-child(5),
      .project-table td:nth-child(5),
      .project-table th:nth-child(6),
      .project-table td:nth-child(6),
      .project-table th:nth-child(7),
      .project-table td:nth-child(7) {
        width: 80px;
      } /* 날짜 필드들 */
      .project-table th:nth-child(8),
      .project-table td:nth-child(8) {
        width: 150px;
      } /* 추가의견 */
      .project-table th:nth-child(9),
      .project-table td:nth-child(9) {
        width: 100px;
      } /* 콘텐츠 */
      .project-table th:nth-child(10),
      .project-table td:nth-child(10) {
        width: 120px;
      } /* 비고 */
      .project-table th:nth-child(11),
      .project-table td:nth-child(11) {
        width: 80px;
        text-align: center;
      } /* HTML 링크 */
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: var(--accent-color);
        color: var(--dark-color);
        padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .btn:hover {
        background-color: #e3b100;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      }

      footer {
        background-color: var(--secondary-color);
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 1rem 0;
        position: relative;
        bottom: 0;
        width: 100%;
      }

      @media (max-width: 1200px) {
        .project-table {
          font-size: 14px;
        }

        .project-table th,
        .project-table td {
          padding: 10px;
        }

        .project-table th {
          font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        .btn {
          padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
          font-size: 0.8rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
</html>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>{title}</h1>
  </header>

  <div class="container">
    <section class="project-info">
      <h2>프로젝트 개요</h2>
      <div class="project-description">
        <p>
          본 프로젝트는 한국은행의 직원 평가 프로세스를 현대화하고 효율화하기
          위해 개발된 종합적인 웹 기반 시스템입니다.
        </p>
        <p>사용된 기술 스택:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>프론트엔드: Astro, CSS3, JavaScript (ES6+)</li>
          <li>추가 라이브러리: jqGrid, Chart.js, D3.js</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="table-container">
      <h2>프로젝트 구성 및 진행 현황</h2>
      <table class="project-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>연번</th>
            <th>1Depth</th>
            <th>2Depth</th>
            <th>Tab-Depth</th>
            <th>퍼블1차</th>
            <th>퍼블수정</th>
            <th>퍼블컨펌</th>
            <th>추가의견</th>
            <th>콘텐츠(기본 유지)</th>
            <th>비고</th>
            <th>HTML 링크</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {
            tableCnt.map((item) => (
              <tr>
                <td>{item.number}</td>
                <td>{item.dapth1 || '-'}</td>
                <td>{item.dapth2 || '-'}</td>
                <td>{item.tabDapth || '-'}</td>
                <td>{item.firstDraft || '-'}</td>
                <td>{item.revised || '-'}</td>
                <td>{item.confirmed || '-'}</td>
                <td>{item.additionalComments || '-'}</td>
                <td>{item.contentStatus || '-'}</td>
                <td>{item.remarks || '-'}</td>
                <td>
                  <a
                    href={`../${item.linkTarget}/${item.htmlLink}`}
                    target="_blank"
                    class="btn"
                  >
                    보기
                  </a>
                </td>
              </tr>
            ))
          }
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>
      &copy; 2024 한국은행 직원평가 시스템 프로젝트 포트폴리오. 모든 권리 보유.
    </p>
  </footer>
</body>
